# Server-side LLM config. Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real
# values; `.env` is gitignored. The server reads these on startup
# (see server/ai/llm.ts).
#
# Auth token. Two names are accepted; the first one found wins.
#   - ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN: alt name used by some Anthropic-compatible
#     proxies (e.g. Chinese providers that expose the Messages API)
#   - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: the official Anthropic SDK default
# For real Anthropic, set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY. For a proxy, set
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN and (usually) ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL.
#
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Override the default base URL. Leave unset to hit the official
# Anthropic endpoint. Set this when using a proxy.
#
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com

# Override the default model. Default is `claude-sonnet-4-6`.
# Proxies expose their own model names (e.g. `MiniMax-M3`).
#
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
